---
title: Homemade Bacon & Basil Pesto Pizza with Courgette & Caramelised Onion
description: This vibrant veggie pizza is inspired by Italy, paying respect to the ingredients and proving that less can often mean more. But we won't blink twice if you want to load up these pizzas with all your favourite toppings like basil pesto and fresh veggies!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65dbe9bd7efc065796209e3c-111e1653.jpeg
